title: Former Arizona WR Tetairoa McMillan wins AP NFL Offensive Rookie of the Year

sources.name: Yahoo Sports NFL
sources.title: Former Arizona WR Tetairoa McMillan wins AP NFL Offensive Rookie of the Year
sources.description: Tetairoa McMillan won his first major award Thursday night, and if his rookie season is any indication, it won’t be his last. The Carolina Panthers receiver took home the AP NFL Offensive Rookie of the Year at the NFL Honors. The former Arizona Wildcats All-American led all rookies with 1,014 receiving yards.
